OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FHeavy
OL,6,Frain clearing on Saturday morning,
OL,7,Fthen cloudy and cooler. Cloudy start
OL,8,Fon Sunday then brightening up with
OL,9,Fsunny intervals. Monday dry and sunny
OL,10,Fand becoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
